title: Keeping Up With The Kardashians S09E16 A Thailand Vacation Part
description: Can the Kardashians learn to get along on the last leg of their trip to Thailand? Plus, will Khloe head back to the States to be with Rob? Then, a trip to visit an orphanage changes their lives forever. Aside from donating toys and clothes, Kim is eager to do more. But when she falls in love with a young girl will her family approve of her idea for adoption? Could North West be getting an older sister? Then, Brody and Brandon are determined to find Khloe a vacation fling! See the final days of their family va-cay.
